    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[Address], [b].[Created], [b].[Note], [b].[Phone], [b].[Status], [b].[Total], [b].[UserId], [r].[UserId], [r].[ConfirmPassword], [r].[Email], [r].[Password], [r].[Role], [r].[UserName], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Price], [t].[Quantity], [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Infor], [t].[Name], [t].[Price0], [t].[ProductString], [t].[Quantity0]
FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[Address], [b].[Created], [b].[Note], [b].[Phone], [b].[Status], [b].[Total], [b].[UserId], [r].[UserId], [r].[ConfirmPassword], [r].[Email], [r].[Password], [r].[Role], [r].[UserName], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Price], [t].[Quantity], [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Infor], [t].[Name], [t].[Price0], [t].[ProductString], [t].[Quantity0]
FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[Address], [b].[Created], [b].[Note], [b].[Phone], [b].[Status], [b].[Total], [b].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Price], [t].[Quantity], [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Infor], [t].[Name], [t].[Price0], [t].[ProductString], [t].[Quantity0]
FROM [Bills] AS [b]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

2023-11-08 10:02:28.859 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (21ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[Address], [b].[Created], [b].[Note], [b].[Phone], [b].[Status], [b].[Total], [b].[UserId], [r].[UserId], [r].[ConfirmPassword], [r].[Email], [r].[Password], [r].[Role], [r].[UserName], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Price], [t].[Quantity], [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Infor], [t].[Name], [t].[Price0], [t].[ProductString], [t].[Quantity0]
FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]

SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[Address], [b].[Created], [b].[Note], [b].[Phone], [b].[Status], [b].[Total], [b].[UserId], [r].[UserId], [r].[ConfirmPassword], [r].[Email], [r].[Password], [r].[Role], [r].[UserName], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Price], [t].[Quantity], [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Infor], [t].[Name], [t].[Price0], [t].[ProductString], [t].[Quantity0]
FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

SELECT [b].[Id], [b].[Address], [b].[Created], [b].[Note], [b].[Phone], [b].[Status], [b].[Total], [b].[UserId], [r].[UserId], [r].[ConfirmPassword], [r].[Email], [r].[Password], [r].[Role], [r].[UserName], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Price], [t].[Quantity], [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Infor], [t].[Name], [t].[Price0], [t].[ProductString], [t].[Quantity0]
FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]

    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
    FROM [BillDetails] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [b].[Id] = [t].[BillId]
ORDER BY [b].[Id], [r].[UserId], [t].[BillId], [t].[ProductId]

FROM [Bills] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Register] AS [r] ON [b].[UserId] = [r].[UserId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[BillId], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Price], [b0].[Quantity], [p].[Id], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Infor], [p].[Name], [p].[Price] AS [Price0], [p].[ProductString], [p].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0]
